>Farewell Ritual + Hospitality</sgkb:inferred_need><sgkb:recommended_message_type>Faith</sgkb:recommended_message_type><sgkb:priority>High</sgkb:priority><sgkb:evidence_required>journey_type is hajj</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>active zone is kaaba, tawaf, or alharam</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>trajectory pattern is tawaf_circular_movement</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>movement trend indicates departure after Tawaf or journey stage is ending</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>user is before departure from Makkah</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:knowledge_intent>tawaf_wadaa_guidance</sgkb:knowledge_intent><sgkb:creator>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:creator><sgkb:title>Tawaf al-Wadaa</sgkb:title><sgkb:data_identifier>TawafAlWadaa</sgkb:data_identifier><sgkb:publisher>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:publisher><sgkb:publication_date>2026-07-11</sgkb:publication_date><sgkb:summary>The farewell Tawaf performed before leaving Makkah at the end of the Hajj journey.</sgkb:summary><sgkb:keywords>Ritual</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>TawafAlWadaa</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>Tawaf al-Wadaa</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>طواف الوداع</sgkb:keywords></owl:NamedIndividual><owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Sai"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Ritual" /><sgkb:label_en>Sa'i</sgkb:label_en><sgkb:label_ar>السعي</sgkb:label_ar><sgkb:definition>The ritual movement between Safa and Marwa.</sgkb:definition><sgkb:definition_ar>السعي نسك يكون بين الصفا والمروة سبعة أشواط، يبدأ من الصفا وينتهي عند المروة.</sgkb:definition_ar><sgkb:ritual_of rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#HajjJourney" /><sgkb:ritual_of rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#UmrahJourney" /><sgkb:follows rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Tawaf" /><sgkb:associated_place rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#SafaMarwa" /><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>safa</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>marwah</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>sai</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:spatial_rule>User is inside or near Safa, Marwa, or the Sa'i path.</sgkb:spatial_rule><sgkb:movement_rule>Directional movement along the Safa-Marwa axis.</sgkb:movement_rule><sgkb:required_rounds>7</sgkb:required_rounds><sgkb:start_zone_id>safa</sgkb:start_zone_id><sgkb:end_zone_id>marwah</sgkb:end_zone_id><sgkb:round_count_rule>Sa'i consists of seven one-way traversals between Safa and Marwa.</sgkb:round_count_rule><sgkb:sequence_rule>Sa'i starts at Safa and ends at Marwah on the seventh traversal.</sgkb:sequence_rule><sgkb:context_state>ritual_performance_state</sgkb:context_state><sgkb:inferred_need>Ritual Performance + Guidance</sgkb:inferred_need><sgkb:recommended_message_type>Guidance</sgkb:recommended_message_type><sgkb:priority>High</sgkb:priority><sgkb:evidence_required>active zone is safa, marwah, or Sa'i path</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>trajectory pattern is sai_directional_movement</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>movement state is walking</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:knowledge_intent>sai_guidance</sgkb:knowledge_intent><sgkb:precedes rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#HairShaving" /><sgkb:creator>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:creator><sgkb:title>Sa'i</sgkb:title><sgkb:data_identifier>Sai</sgkb:data_identifier><sgkb:publisher>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:publisher><sgkb:publication_date>2026-07-11</sgkb:publication_date><sgkb:summary>The ritual movement between Safa and Marwa.</sgkb:summary><sgkb:keywords>Ritual</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>Sai</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>Sa'i</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>السعي</sgkb:keywords></owl:NamedIndividual><owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#StandingInArafat"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Ritual" /><sgkb:label_en>Standing in Arafat</sgkb:label_en><sgkb:label_ar>الوقوف بعرفة</sgkb:label_ar><sgkb:definition>The Hajj ritual of being present in Arafat on the ninth day of the Islamic month of Dhu al-Hijjah, with the pilgrim remaining in Arafat until sunset.</sgkb:definition><sgkb:definition_ar>الوقوف بعرفة هو حضور الحاج في عرفة في اليوم التاسع من ذي الحجة، ويبقى فيها إلى غروب الشمس.</sgkb:definition_ar><sgkb:ritual_of rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#HajjJourney" /><sgkb:follows rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Sai" /><sgkb:associated_place rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#ArafatPlace" /><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>arafat</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>jabal_al_rahmah</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>namirah_mosque</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>jabal_namirah</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>mashair_train_arafat_3_station</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:temporal_rule>{"calendar": "Hijri", "month": "Dhu al-Hijjah", "day": 9, "until": "sunset", "followed_by": "MuzdalifahNight"}</sgkb:temporal_rule><sgkb:spatial_rule>User is inside or near Arafat-related geofences on the ninth day of Dhu al-Hijjah during the Hajj journey, and remains there until sunset before proceeding to Muzdalifah.</sgkb:spatial_rule><sgkb:movement_rule>May include stationary presence, slow movement, or limited movement within Arafat-related zones.</sgkb:movement_rule><sgkb:context_state>standing_in_arafat_state</sgkb:context_state><sgkb:inferred_need>Spiritual Reflection + Reassurance</sgkb:inferred_need><sgkb:recommended_message_type>Faith</sgkb:recommended_message_type><sgkb:priority>High</sgkb:priority><sgkb:evidence_required>journey_type is hajj</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>Hijri date is 9 Dhu al-Hijjah</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>active zone is Arafat-related</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>time is before or at sunset on Day of Arafat</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>user is inside, near, or stationary within Arafat-related geofences</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:knowledge_intent>standing_arafat_reflection</sgkb:knowledge_intent><sgkb:notes>This node models the ritual act, while DayOfArafat models the religious occasion.</sgkb:notes><sgkb:mentioned_in_quran rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#QuranVerse_2_198" /><sgkb:creator>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:creator><sgkb:title>Standing in Arafat</sgkb:title><sgkb:data_identifier>StandingInArafat</sgkb:data_identifier><sgkb:publisher>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:publisher><sgkb:publication_date>2026-07-11</sgkb:publication_date><sgkb:summary>The Hajj ritual of being present in Arafat on the ninth day of the Islamic month of Dhu al-Hijjah, with the pilgrim remaining in Arafat until sunset.</sgkb:summary><sgkb:keywords>Ritual</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>StandingInArafat</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>Standing in Arafat</sgkb:keywords><sgkb:keywords>الوقوف بعرفة</sgkb:keywords></owl:NamedIndividual><owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#SpendingNightInMuzdalifah"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Ritual" /><sgkb:label_en>Spending the night in Muzdalifah</sgkb:label_en><sgkb:label_ar>المبيت بمزدلفة</sgkb:label_ar><sgkb:definition>The Hajj ritual state of remaining in Muzdalifah, whose time begins after sunset on the Day of Arafat and continues through the night before the tenth day of Dhu al-Hijjah.</sgkb:definition><sgkb:definition_ar>يبدأ وقت الوقوف والمبيت بمزدلفة من بعد غروب شمس يوم عرفة، ويمتد خلال الليلة التي تسبق اليوم العاشر من ذي الحجة.</sgkb:definition_ar><sgkb:ritual_of rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#HajjJourney" /><sgkb:follows rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#StandingInArafat" /><sgkb:precedes rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#Rami" /><sgkb:associated_place rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#MuzdalifahPlace" /><sgkb:associated_occasion rdf:resource="https://github.com/ghadairesearch/SacredGeoKB#MuzdalifahNight" /><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>muzdalifah</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:associated_zone_ids>mashair_train_muzdalifah_station</sgkb:associated_zone_ids><sgkb:temporal_rule>{"calendar": "Hijri", "month": "Dhu al-Hijjah", "day": 9, "starts_after": "sunset_on_day_of_arafat", "time_window": "after_sunset_to_fajr", "next_day": 10}</sgkb:temporal_rule><sgkb:spatial_rule>User is inside or near Muzdalifah-related geofences after leaving Arafat and before proceeding to Mina or the Jamarat.</sgkb:spatial_rule><sgkb:movement_rule>Stationary presence, very limited movement, or repeated location samples within Muzdalifah during the night window.</sgkb:movement_rule><sgkb:context_state>muzdalifah_overnight_state</sgkb:context_state><sgkb:inferred_need>Rest + Ritual Reassurance</sgkb:inferred_need><sgkb:recommended_message_type>Hospitality</sgkb:recommended_message_type><sgkb:priority>High</sgkb:priority><sgkb:evidence_required>journey_type is hajj</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>time is after sunset on Day of Arafat or night before 10 Dhu al-Hijjah</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>active zone is Muzdalifah-related</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:evidence_required>user is stationary or moving within a limited radius in Muzdalifah</sgkb:evidence_required><sgkb:knowledge_intent>muzdalifah_overnight_guidance</sgkb:knowledge_intent><sgkb:notes>This node models the ritual act of spending the night in Muzdalifah after Arafat, while MuzdalifahNight models the corresponding religious time window.</sgkb:notes><sgkb:creator>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:creator><sgkb:title>Spending the night in Muzdalifah</sgkb:title><sgkb:data_identifier>SpendingNightInMuzdalifah</sgkb:data_identifier><sgkb:publisher>Ghader Kurdi</sgkb:publisher><sgkb:publication_date>2026-0